title: Thousands In Berlin Protest Plan For Trans-Atlantic Trade Agreement
text:
sharethis 10/12/15 6:15am At least 150,000 people marched in Berlin on Saturday to protest a planned free trade deal between Europe and the United States that they say is anti-democratic and will lower standards for food safety, labor and the environment. Organizers - an alliance of environmental groups, charities and opposition parties - said 250,000 people had taken partâ€¦ Berlin protests , TPP Comments
